{"tid":151588,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"直擊深圳分店　打邊爐送修甲睇變臉　200人仔埋單","createTime":"2017-03-11T04:20:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-11T05:13:29.000Z","uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ee488af5d3dd3207558159d6475125a0d6c924e","tid":151588,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T04:20:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hk01.com/article/76310\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F76310&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRmMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=c1836e6e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk01.com/article/76310</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=8ZYUqZMwTms\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8ZYUqZMwTms&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRmMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=29737f51\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=8ZYUqZMwTms</a><br />\n<br />\n來自四川的火鍋連鎖店「海底撈」，據報將落戶油麻地。這間以服務為賣點的火鍋店奉行客人至上，除打邊爐外免費提供修甲、擦鞋等服務，卻被網民戲謔是「變態服務」。<br />\n到底「海底撈」服務有多厲害？《香港01》上周五（3日）到深圳福田分店親身體驗，發現修甲、擦鞋只是開端，更「變態」的是有店員表演中國國粹變臉、一人打邊爐嫌悶有三呎毛公仔「陪坐」、女士遇月事更有湯水奉上，十多項服務連食物盛惠每人200元人民幣，划不划算見人見智。不過要在人力及舖租成本出名高的香港經營，「海底撈」能站穩陣腳嗎？"},{"pid":"e42be60ad4cbbf91dde7f9f31d3039606b02a777","tid":151588,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T05:13:29.000Z","msg":"呢到有最底工資喎"}]}